Difficulty: 0/10 Hardness: Copy Paste is all you have to worry about. Credits: 100% You the Viewers/ Users
[center][size=24pt]First:[/size][/center]
[ul][li]Go to your source, Example: "vaginascape Source " [/li] [li]Go to: [/li][/ul]
[IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/t8sv1z.jpg[/img]
[ul][li] src\com\rs\game\player.java..... [ Should be around their. ][/li] [li]Open it with Notepad or Notepad ++ or what you use is no matter.[/li] [li]Search:[/li] [li] if(username.equalsIgnoreCase[/li][/ul]
[IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/33krfjq.jpg[/img]
[ul][li] The: rights = 2; Is the owner number or Jagex Admin #[/li] [li]Don't change that unless your is different.[/li] [li]Change the Mod_Carlos or anything listed on this picture.[/li] [li] If you are going to use mine in the near future you will get crased[/li][/ul]
HENCE: [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/33krfjq.jpg[/img]
[size=14pt]Compile, and then run and then you are the number 1 coder of the future![/size]
[center][size=24pt]Explanations:[/size][/center]
The rights = #; 735 rights listed below:
[ul][li]1 = Mod[/li] [li]2 = Admin or Owner[/li] [li]0 = Player[/li] [li]Their can be more but this is only for 735.[/li][/ul]
Please remember to always put: King_Carlos on: every space: _ This can sometimes miss it up and not make you mod or whatever. Example:
[ul][li]vagina_suck[/li] [li]I_suck_dick[/li] [li]nig_the_boss[/li][/ul]
